      "type": "text",
      "x": 400,
      "y": 240,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "text": "Beam = {A, B} kept both E’s neighbors.\nExpanded A: added C, D to beam.\nExpanded B: also found D!\nD confirmed via 2 paths → returned. ✓",
